The '''East Germany national handball team''' was the national team of the former country [[East Germany]]. The team participated in international [[team handball]] competitions, and had eight appearances at the [[World Men's Handball Championship]], where they won silver medals in [[1970 World Men's Handball Championship|1970]] and [[1974 World Men's Handball Championship|1974]], and bronze medals in [[1978 World Men's Handball Championship|1978]] and [[1986 World Men's Handball Championship|1986]].

